# Documentation Rules

- Write in plain, precise language for patients, contributors, and reviewers.
- Keep privacy, consent, patient control, and non-diagnostic AI limits visible.
- Prefer durable project facts over session-specific notes.
- Match the structure and voice of nearby documents.
